To use graphical plugins, you need to have on your server :

- RRDTOOL
- perl/RRDTOOL (RRDs.pm)
- Net::SNMP

To use Centreon, you need to have on your server :

- php5
- php-mysql
- php-pear
- php-snmp
- php-posix
- php-gd
- php-ldap (if you would like to use LDAP authentification)
- gd-devel
- libpng
- libpng-devel
- perl-config-IniFiles
- perl-Crypt-DES
- perl-Digest-HMAC
- perl-Digest-SHA1
- perl-GD
- perl-IO-Socket-INET6
- perl-Net-SNMP
- perl-rrdtool
- perl-Socket6

FRANCAIS :
----------

Pour installer Oreon sans mise à jour :

	Lancer la commande "./install.sh"

ENGLISH :
---------

For install only :

	Launch "./install.sh"

For more information :
- mail infos@centreon.com
- visit Centreon's forum http://forum.centreon.com
- visit Centreon's Wiki http://wiki.centreon.com

Thanks for using Centreon.
